        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1628-03-04T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1628-03-04T00:00:00-05:00" n="5" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d5">
                <head>[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#center">
                        <hi rend="italic">Extract from the charter
                                    of Massachusetts Bay</hi>, <hi rend="italic">granted by Charles
                                    I of England</hi>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1628-03-04">
                            <hi rend="italic">March</hi> 4, 1628</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>* * * * * “We do give and grant all the Landes and Hereditaments within
                            the Space of Three English Miles to the southward of Massachusetts Bay:
                            and all those Landes and Hereditaments within the Space of Three English
                            Miles to the Northward of the River called Merrimack, all Landes and
                            Hereditaments whatsoever, lying within the Lymitts aforesaide, North and
                            South in Latitude and Bredth, and in Length and Longitude, of and within
                            all the Bredth aforesaide, throughout the mayne Landes there, from the
                            Atlantick and Westerne Sea and Ocean on the East Parte, to the South Sea
                            on the West Parte.”</p>
                <p rend="center">* * * * * * *</p>
            </div>
